title: Fox Presents | EYEWEAR 2014
description:
Born from 40 years of product innovation, Fox Eyewear is unmatched in quality and style. World leading Optics by Carl Zeiss Vision lens technology and premium quality frame materials and components are combined to create bold styles that are as unique as the personalities who wear them. This is Fox Eyewear. For more on Eyewear check out:http://www.foxhead.com/eyewear
